---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us" description="Meet Frank and learn about The Shutter Guy's 35+ years of experience in window treatments and construction throughout the East Coast and St. Petersburg, FL.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-800 text-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">About The Shutter Guy</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
          35+ years of experience. From the Hamptons to St. Petersburg. Your local window treatment specialist.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Meet Frank Video -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <span class="text-primary-600 font-semibold">Meet Frank</span>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-2 mb-6">
            The Shutter Guy Himself
          </h2>
          <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600">
            <p>
              We've lived and worked in the Hamptons in Long Island, NY, New Jersey, and now St. Petersburg. 
              Each location has provided us extensive experience in all aspects of renovation and construction.
            </p>
            <p>
              With over 35 years in the construction field, we know window treatments inside and out. 
              We extended our expertise to include guidance on, as well as installation of, shutters, 
              blinds, and shades for your home or office.
            </p>
            <p>
              When you work with The Shutter Guy, you work directly with me ‚Äî not a sales team. 
              I'll give you honest advice based on your needs, your space, and your budget. 
              No pressure, no gimmicks.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Facebook Video Embed -->
          <div class="aspect-video rounded-2xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden bg-gray-900">
            <iframe 
              src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftheshutterguystpete%2Fvideos%2F401205764096666%2F&show_text=false&width=560" 
              width="100%" 
              height="100%" 
              style="border:none;overflow:hidden" 
              scrolling="no" 
              frameborder="0" 
              allowfullscreen="true" 
              allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture; web-share"
              class="w-full h-full">
            </iframe>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-primary-600 text-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <p class="text-4xl font-bold">35+</p>
            <p class="text-primary-100">Years Experience</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Why Choose Us</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          We're not a big-box store or a franchise. We're your neighbor ‚Äî and we treat every customer's home like our own.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Locally Manufactured</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Our products are made right here by the best in the industry ‚Äî not shipped from overseas. 
            This means better quality control and faster turnaround times.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">25-Year Warranty</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We stand behind our work with an industry-leading warranty. When we install shutters, 
            we expect them to last a lifetime ‚Äî and we guarantee it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Fair Pricing</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            No high-pressure sales tactics or inflated prices. We provide honest quotes and help you 
            find solutions that fit your budget without sacrificing quality.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HERO Discount -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-amber-600">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8">
        <div class="text-center md:text-left">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start space-x-3 mb-4">
            <span class="text-4xl">üéñÔ∏è</span>
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-black">HERO Discount</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-amber-900 max-w-xl mb-4">
            We're proud to honor those who serve our community with <strong>10% off</strong> your entire order.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center md:justify-start">
            <span class="bg-amber-700 text-white text-sm font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Active Military</span>
            <span class="bg-amber-700 text-white text-sm font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Veterans</span>
            <span class="bg-amber-700 text-white text-sm font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Police</span>
            <span class="bg-amber-700 text-white text-sm font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Fire & EMT</span>
            <span class="bg-amber-700 text-white text-sm font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Nurses</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-black text-white rounded-xl p-6 mb-4">
            <p class="text-5xl font-bold">10%</p>
            <p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold">OFF</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-black font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition inline-flex items-center whitespace-nowrap">
            Claim Your Discount
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Ready to Meet?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        I'd love to visit your home, discuss your needs, and show you what's possible. 
        Schedule your free consultation today.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="bg-primary-600 text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition inline-flex items-center justify-center">
        Schedule Free Consultation
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
